\id 3JN - Muinane NT -Colombia 2009 (DBL -2013) 
\h 3 SAN JUAN AAME 
\toc1 3 San Juan Aame 
\toc2 3 San Juan Aame 
\toc3 3 Jn 
\mt1 3 SAN JUAN AAME 
\c 1  
\s1 Gayo Onoobotɨ, Imino Ihiimaano. 
\p  
\v 1 Uujoho quillahutoobo iicaabo caatɨnɨhi jihaameque agaijɨɨbo tañahabo Gayodi, diiboco miyanotɨro agaijɨɨbedi. 
\p  
\v 2 Agaijɨɨbo tañahabo, dihallɨvɨ Moocaanima iimaahicahi. Fanoova ɨɨma imino ifeequi tollɨro guihuvatɨɨbo diicaqui, bu oono imino dijeebɨɨ ofoobadɨ diicaqui icano.  
\v 3 Mɨɨro saatoho monahabomɨ asaaumo imino dijeebɨɨ miyaanofañodɨ iicanoco, bu imino jɨɨbogo onoobadɨ idiicanoco icano ɨjɨɨbuguunoco uguubuhinɨɨboro imo imo icahi.  
\v 4 Jaano toonobadɨ chahahi sanooba uco imo imo iminiiyuno. Jino, taseeme, miyaanofañodɨ imino mɨhɨgonoco guubuhi. 
\p  
\v 5 Agaijɨɨbo tañahabo, imino aivo moonɨhicahi monahabomɨco adaamusuubo sihɨgotɨ asaamoco adaamusunofeenedɨ aivo imino moonɨhicahi.  
\v 6 Jaanoco diito Moocaani iijanomɨnaafeenevɨ jɨɨbeguehicahi ɨɨjoho sihidɨ gaijɨma idiicanoco. Jaanegui diitoco imino daamusu, ucuujɨvaachunehejeque daacɨ imino ifeequi, Moocaani imogobadɨ.  
\v 7 Mɨɨro diito Cristo dudɨcamaajeguiiha ɨɨgomo. Jaamo imogotɨhi Moocaanico agaajatɨmo aacɨnehejeque agaayɨcɨnoco.  
\v 8 Jaaneguiiha mɨɨhai diitoco imino momoonɨnofeenedɨ mahamusuqui iimino jɨɨbogoco. 
\s1 Diotrefe Onoobo Imitɨno Iicano. 
\p  
\v 9 Uujoho caatɨnɨuhi aameque Moocaani iijamɨnaadi. Jaarunoco Diotrefe guubuutɨhi mɨɨhai iijɨco, diitofeenevɨ aivojɨɨbotɨ iicanoco imogooboro.  
\v 10 Jaaneguiiha ofoohachiijɨ faamo ɨmefeenevɨro neeji: Mɨɨhaiditɨ sɨcamañooco ihiimaaboro abañɨhicanoco, bu tollɨro monahabomɨ tahɨ ɨɨfotomoco gaayɨcɨhicatɨɨbo, bu agaayɨcɨgomoco gaayɨcɨsuhicatɨɨbo icano. Jaaboro Moocaani iijatɨ diitoco gañɨɨhicaabo. 
\p  
\v 11 Jaaneguiiha agaijɨɨbo tañahabo, diito imitɨno omoonɨbadɨ diicadino iminoro diica. Mɨɨro iiminoco omoonɨɨbo, Moocaanitahe. Jaanotɨ iimitɨnoco omoonɨɨbo, Moocaanico atyɨmetɨhiica. 
\s1 Demetrio Imino Omoonɨno. 
\p  
\v 12 Jaanotɨ famooro Demetriotɨ imino iimaahicahi. Jaano miyaanofeenedɨ gaajacafetehi. Jaanoco mɨɨhai bu tollɨro mɨjɨɨbeguehi. Bu jaanoco amɨɨhai magaajahi miyaano iicanoco. 
\s1 Niino Iimaa. 
\p  
\v 13 Sihidɨ ɨco neejirahi. Jaaruubo imogotɨhi caatɨnɨtafaihu, bu caatɨnɨtai icanofeenedɨ eheetavonoco.  
\v 14 Imeguehi goovano ɨco aatyɨmeneque. Jaadɨ jari mihiimaacasiji faño. 
\p  
\v 15 Jaanegui sajeebɨɨ diica. Juuga nahabomɨ dijaa iijɨco galluuhi. Ɨɨjoho bu paryɨ famooro monahabomɨco moojɨco daacɨ.